trpzClusterMib.name: trpzClusterMib
trpzClusterMib.contactinfo: Trapeze Networks Technical Support www.trapezenetworks.com US: 866.TRPZ.TAC International: 925.474.2400 support@trapezenetworks.com
trpzClusterMib.description: Cluster objects for Trapeze Networks wireless switches. AP = Access Point; AC = Access Controller (wireless switch), the device that runs a SNMP Agent implementing this MIB; PAM = Primary AP Manager; SAM = Secondary AP Manager. trpzClusterApAssignmentTable.name: trpzClusterApAssignmentTable
trpzClusterApAssignmentTable.description: A table describing the AP manager assignments for the APs currently present and managed by the Cluster this AC is part of.

trpzClusterApAssignmentEntry.name: trpzClusterApAssignmentEntry
trpzClusterApAssignmentEntry.description: Information about a particular AP assignment in this Cluster.

trpzClusterApAssignPamIp.name: trpzClusterApAssignPamIp
trpzClusterApAssignPamIp.description: The IP address of the assigned Primary AP Manager controller.

trpzClusterApAssignSamIp.name: trpzClusterApAssignSamIp
trpzClusterApAssignSamIp.description: The IP address of the assigned Secondary AP Manager controller. A value of 0.0.0.0 means this AP does not have an assigned SAM.

trpzClusterApAssignConnectedToPam.name: trpzClusterApAssignConnectedToPam
trpzClusterApAssignConnectedToPam.description: Indicates whether this AP is currently connected to its assigned Primary AP Manager controller.

trpzClusterApAssignConnectedToSam.name: trpzClusterApAssignConnectedToSam
trpzClusterApAssignConnectedToSam.description: Indicates whether this AP is currently connected to its assigned Secondary AP Manager controller.

trpzClusterCompliance.name: trpzClusterCompliance
trpzClusterCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that implement Cluster MIB. This compliance statement is for releases 7.5 and greater of AC (wireless switch) software.

trpzClusterApAssignmentGroup.name: trpzClusterApAssignmentGroup
trpzClusterApAssignmentGroup.description: Group of columnar objects implemented to provide Cluster AP Assignments info in releases 7.5 and greater.
